trans-unit.source: An abstract class for creating a custom activity with imperative behavior defined with the <xref:System.Activities.CodeActivity.Execute*> method, which gives access to variable and argument resolution and extensions.
trans-unit.target: En abstrakt klasse for å opprette en egendefinert aktivitet med viktig virkemåte definert med den <xref:System.Activities.CodeActivity.Execute*>metode, som gir tilgang til variabelen og argumentet oppløsning og -utvidelser.</xref:System.Activities.CodeActivity.Execute*>

trans-unit.source: When implemented in a derived class, creates an instance of the derived class.
trans-unit.target: Når implementert i en avledet klasse, oppretter du en forekomst av den utledede klassen.

trans-unit.source: Not implemented.
trans-unit.target: Ikke implementert.

trans-unit.source: Use <xref:System.Activities.CodeActivity.CacheMetadata*> instead.
trans-unit.target: Bruk <xref:System.Activities.CodeActivity.CacheMetadata*>i stedet.</xref:System.Activities.CodeActivity.CacheMetadata*>

trans-unit.source: Custom activity authors can provide validation logic in an activity's <xref:System.Activities.CodeActivity.CacheMetadata%2A> override.
trans-unit.target: Egendefinert aktivitet forfattere kan gi validering logikken i en aktivitet <xref:System.Activities.CodeActivity.CacheMetadata%2A>overstyre.</xref:System.Activities.CodeActivity.CacheMetadata%2A>

trans-unit.source: Any exceptions that are thrown from <xref:System.Activities.CodeActivity.CacheMetadata%2A> are not treated as validation errors.
trans-unit.target: Unntak som er et fra <xref:System.Activities.CodeActivity.CacheMetadata%2A>behandles ikke som valideringsfeil.</xref:System.Activities.CodeActivity.CacheMetadata%2A>

trans-unit.source: These exceptions will escape from the call to <xref:System.Activities.Validation.ActivityValidationServices.Validate%2A> and must be handled by the caller.
trans-unit.target: Disse unntakene skal Escape-kode fra kall til <xref:System.Activities.Validation.ActivityValidationServices.Validate%2A>og må behandles oppkalleren.</xref:System.Activities.Validation.ActivityValidationServices.Validate%2A>

trans-unit.source: Not implemented.
trans-unit.target: Ikke implementert.

trans-unit.source: Creates and validates a description of the activity’s arguments, variables, child activities, and activity delegates.
trans-unit.target: Oppretter og validerer en beskrivelse av for aktiviteten argumenter variabler, underordnede aktiviteter og aktiviteter representanter.

trans-unit.source: The workflow runtime uses the default implementation of CacheMetadata to ensure correct construction of a workflow as well as to manage runtime relationships and lifetime rules.
trans-unit.target: Kjøretiden arbeidsflyten bruker standard implementering av CacheMetadata slik at riktige konstruksjon av en arbeidsflyt i tillegg til å administrere runtime relasjoner og levetid regler.

trans-unit.source: The default implementation of CacheMetadata examines the public members of the activity type using the type’s <xref:System.ComponentModel.TypeDescriptor>.
trans-unit.target: Standard implementering av CacheMetadata undersøker offentlige medlemmene av aktivitetstypen ved bruk av typen <xref:System.ComponentModel.TypeDescriptor>.</xref:System.ComponentModel.TypeDescriptor>

trans-unit.source: These public members are of type <xref:System.Activities.Argument>, <xref:System.Activities.Variable>, [T:System.Collections.Generic.IEnumerable\<T:System.Activities.Variable>](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md), <xref:System.Activities.Activity>, [T:System.Collections.Generic.IEnumerable\<T:System.Activities.Activity>](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md), or <xref:System.Activities.ActivityDelegate>.
trans-unit.target: Disse offentlige medlemmene er av typen <xref:System.Activities.Argument>, <xref:System.Activities.Variable>, [T:System.Collections.Generic.IEnumerable\<T:System.Activities.Variable >](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md), <xref:System.Activities.Activity>, [T:System.Collections.Generic.IEnumerable\<T:System.Activities.Activity >](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md), eller <xref:System.Activities.ActivityDelegate>.</xref:System.Activities.ActivityDelegate> </xref:System.Activities.Activity> </xref:System.Activities.Variable> </xref:System.Activities.Argument>

trans-unit.source: You can override this method to customize the building of the activity’s run-time description and to provide custom validation logic.
trans-unit.target: Du kan overstyre denne metoden tilpasse byggingen av aktivitetens kjøretid beskrivelse, og angi egendefinert validering logic.

trans-unit.source: Any exceptions that are thrown from CacheMetadata are not treated as validation errors.
trans-unit.target: Unntak som er et fra CacheMetadata behandles ikke som valideringsfeil.

trans-unit.source: These exceptions will escape from the call to <xref:System.Activities.Validation.ActivityValidationServices.Validate%2A> and must be handled by the caller.
trans-unit.target: Disse unntakene skal Escape-kode fra kall til <xref:System.Activities.Validation.ActivityValidationServices.Validate%2A>og må behandles oppkalleren.</xref:System.Activities.Validation.ActivityValidationServices.Validate%2A>
